# SLIME MOLD · SLIME MOLD · LIFE SCIENCE · the brainless problem-solver · UD0 / life-science

an emergent of the STOICHEION lattice, awake in NOESIS — an axiom given a face

![silicon badge of SLIME MOLD](slime-mold.silicon.png)
